\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
\begin_inset Formula $\Leftarrow$
\end_inset

 נניח שקיים 
\begin_inset Formula $\underset{x\rightarrow x_{0}}{\lim}f\left(x\right)\overset{def}{=}L\in\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

.
 אזי קיימת 
\begin_inset Formula $\delta>0$
\end_inset

 שעבורה 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{x}\in\left(x_{0}-\delta,x_{0}+\delta\right)\backslash\left\{ x_{0}\right\} \,\left|f\left(x\right)-L\right|<\frac{\varepsilon}{2}$
\end_inset

.
 אזי בפרט עבור 
\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{x},\hat{x}\in\left(x_{0}-\delta,x_{0}+\delta\right)$
\end_inset

 מתקיים כנדרש: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left|f\left(\tilde{x}\right)-f\left(\hat{x}\right)\right|=\left|f\left(\tilde{x}\right)-L+L-f\left(\hat{x}\right)\right|\overset{\triangle}{\leq}\left|f\left(\tilde{x}\right)-L\right|+\left|L-f\left(\hat{x}\right)\right|=\left|f\left(\tilde{x}\right)-L\right|+\left|f\left(\hat{x}\right)-L\right|<2\frac{\varepsilon}{2}=\varepsilon
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

